response.overview: Mockumentary family adventure taking its cue from the YouTube viral video sensation. An Australian zoologist travels to China to find the baby panda - whose sneeze has been watched over 250 million times - in the hope that the star attraction will revitalise her ailing zoo.
response.tagline: The movie inspired by the YouTube sensation!
response.title: Sneezing Baby Panda: The Movie

titles.title: The Life and Times of Sneezing Baby Panda
